I gave a presentation today (29th of August) at ESA2020 titled *Attributions for poverty in Post-Socialist Countries* in a session *Rethinking and Theorizing the Experience of Transformations in Eastern and Central European Societies*. Thank you everyone for the comments! [Click here to access the presentation slides](http://markuskainu.fi/material/presentation/TorinoSlides2013_final.html)

